Mike Elliott (comedian) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Elliott_(comedian) 0 Michael Elliott (17 July 1946 – 23 December 2014), also known as Mike the Mouth, was an English stand-up comedian, actor, television presenter, radio personality and comedian.On 23 December 2014 Elliott died of esophageal cancer at age 68.
